name: Kitty Fly Home
description:
Help a lost space cat get back home to his dad! Navigate through 12 levels to make it back safe and sound!

Tip: Knowing when to have your rocket engine off is just as important as knowing when to have it on. Your momentum is conserved in space, so you don't need to keep your engine on to keep moving forward. Flying through the entire level as fast as possible is tricky! Take it slow and careful if you're having trouble!

Controls

  • W or Up Arrow: Increase rocket power
  • S or Down Arrow: Decrease rocket power
  • A/D or Left/Right Arrow: Rotate ship
  • R: Reset level
